label: A2B_mC48_15_4f_2f-001
title: $\alpha$-SnF$_{2}$ Structure
comments: SnF$_{2}$ is found in three structures: \begin{itemize} \item \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B_mC48_15_4f_2f-001}{monoclinic $\alpha$-SnF$_{2}$} (this structure), the ground state \item \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B_oP12_19_2a_a-002}{orthorhombic $\beta$-SnF$_{2}$}, formed from $\gamma$-SnF$_{2}$ on cooling below $67^{\circ}$C, and \item tetragonal $\gamma$-SnF$_{2}$, produced by heating $\alpha$-SnF$_{2}$ above $180^{\circ}C$, forming in the \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B_tP12_92_b_a-002}{$\alpha$-TeO$_{2}$ structure}. \end{itemize}
